# Intentionally empty.
#
# The API serves no static assets, every request is rewritten to the
# serverless function (api/index.js). But Vercel's generic builder (framework:
# null + a custom buildCommand) requires an Output Directory to exist after the
# build, or it fails with "No Output Directory named public found". This empty
# dir satisfies that check; the serverless functions in api/ deploy regardless.
